com.mappedin.sdk

Class Category

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mappedin.sdk.Category

  • public class Category
extends java.lang.Object
    A Category is a collection of similar Locations, which may have parent or children categories. For example, you may have a Fashion category, which a Men’s Fashion and Women’s Fashion category. A Men’s clothing store would belong to the Men’s Fashion category, but not necessarily be present in the Fashion category’s list of Locations.
